            <thetext>IS:

Developers only have the possibility to choose out of 3 mobile themes: Indigo, iOS, Android.

SHOULD:

Developers should be able to modify the indigo in color and main style attribute. This gives the user the possibility to easily customize the styling for every qx.Mobile app.

There should be only single file with all styling variables, which can be modified.</thetext>
